Map Name: aim_colt_ak_cold
Version: 1.0

Description: Based on the original aim_ak_colt for Counter-Strike 1.6.
There have been many re-makes.. but not a snowy one. I know the textures aren't great!
But to be honest, the reason why everybody loves aim_ak_colt is because of its simplicity.
Extract the .RAR File to your cstrike folder within your steamapps. There is also a .NAV for BOTs!
Enjoy!

Credits to: [DnV]Cross for bringing the original aim_ak_colt from CS 1.6 to Counter-Strike Source to allow us to Create even greater versions!
www.hellclan.co.uk

Made by : ]HeLL[ Kyanite
